definitions.definition: The process of shedding or losing a covering of fur , feathers or skin etc.
examples: Some birds change colour during their winter moult .

definitions.definition: The skin or feathers cast off during the process of moulting.

main_definition: The process of shedding or losing a covering of fur , feathers or skin etc.
secondary_definitions: The skin or feathers cast off during the process of moulting.
